{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/Steam_Desc_01.gif?t=1732640812\" />On an isolated island shrouded in fog, an archaeologist is tasked with understanding more about the archipelago's past. In this first-person experience, you'll face your survival instincts filled with psychological terror.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/Steam_Desc_02.gif?t=1732640812\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The silence here is as deafening as the crashing waves of the ocean. As the player explores the island, they will be guided by a growing sense of unease, with a constant feeling that something is watching, always one step ahead, always observing.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/Steam_Desc_04.gif?t=1732640812\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With each discovery, the player will feel the weight of mounting tension. The fear here doesn't come from monsters leaping out of the shadows, but from the gradual realization that the island is more alive than it seems.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/Steam_Desc_03.gif?t=1732640812\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mysterious sounds, flickering lights, and glimpses of figures will make the player question what is real. Prepare to face solitude, the unknown, and an ever-present sense of danger. The island holds secrets, but be warned: sometimes, silence is the best answer.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732640812","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/page.bg.jpg?t=1732640812","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto